---
layout: showcase.njk
title: Grow the ZAVA app addressable market from 10% to 95% of the German market.
description: Expanding ZAVA's German GP booking flow to support statutory health insured patients while maintaining conversion and clarity.
outcomes:
  - "**Opened ~85% of the German GP market** by enabling SHI bookings in the app."
  - "**Maintained ~75% registration conversion** despite a significantly longer, more complex flow."
  - "Post-release **support contact rate stayed below 2.5%**, indicating the flow was clear enough to navigate without help."
problem: ZAVA needed to expand the booking flow for their GP video consultation app in Germany. Expanding the flow to allow bookings with statutory health insured (SHI) GPs would increase the addressable market by ~85%, but would add considerable complexity to the flow.
learnings:
  - "I still found facilitating workshops with senior stakeholders challenging at this stage. Since then I've been doing more focused group workshops when I need stakeholders to collaborate, and 1-1 expert interviews prior to workshops to save time and focus group discussion."
---

